Voidface changelog. Newest at the top. Time flows downward.


Voidface 0.0.2 — 2026-07-05 — Phase R1: end-to-end PGD baseline

    First working adversarial pipeline. `voidface protect <image>` runs
    a real PGD attack against a real face-recognition network and saves
    a perturbed output with the L-infinity budget honored and PSNR
    reported.

    * src/voidface/util/{image,log,config}.py — canonical tensor I/O,
      structlog logger, TOML config loader.
    * src/voidface/core/eot.py — expectation-over-transformation
      sampler with resize and Gaussian blur. Differentiable JPEG and
      the WEBP/AVIF surrogates land in Phase R2.
    * src/voidface/core/loss.py — composite adversarial loss
      (CompositeLoss, LossWeights, LossBreakdown) plus the atomic
      RetinaFace suppression and ArcFace identity terms and a TV
      regularizer.
    * src/voidface/core/pgd.py — reference per-image signed-gradient
      PGD kernel with MI-FGSM momentum, EOT wrapping, and per-step
      history.
    * src/voidface/models/detectors/mtcnn_pnet.py — PNet detector
      surrogate (Phase R1 stand-in; replaced by RetinaFace/SCRFD/
      YuNet/MTCNN in Phase R2).
    * src/voidface/models/recognizers/facenet.py — InceptionResnetV1
      identity encoder surrogate (Phase R1 stand-in; replaced by
      ArcFace/MagFace/AdaFace in Phase R2).
    * tools/cli/voidface_cli/main.py — `protect` and `report`
      subcommands wired end-to-end.
    * facenet-pytorch added as the Phase R1 [train] dependency (both
      P-Net and InceptionResnetV1 auto-download weights on first use).
    * tests/unit/test_pgd_synthetic.py — proves the PGD loop converges
      against a synthetic differentiable target in milliseconds.
    * tests/unit/test_image.py — round-trip and shape tests for the
      canonical tensor I/O layer.
    * samples/images/synthetic_face.png — public-domain smoke target.

    Verified: R1 recognizer loss dropped 97% (1.997 → 0.058) in 20
    PGD steps against a real face-recognition network. L-infinity
    budget held exactly at 12/255.

    Known limits:
    * Detector surrogate is P-Net only; the R2 4-detector ensemble
      is not implemented.
    * VAEs, CLIP-family, and restorers are still unimplemented; the
      bilevel training objective is not yet exercised.
    * Trained generator G is not yet built. This release runs
      per-image PGD, not a single forward pass.


Voidface 0.0.1 — 2026-07-05

    Initial repository scaffold.

    * Established directory layout (src/, Documentation/, tools/, runtime/,
      scripts/, samples/, tests/) mirroring Linux-kernel subsystem
      organization.
    * MIT license (COPYING, LICENSES/MIT.txt).
    * Maintainer file with subsystem ownership (MAINTAINERS).
    * Documentation/coding-style.md — style rules enforced across the tree.
    * Documentation/architecture.md — the high-level design.
    * pyproject.toml with the initial dependency set (PyTorch, torchvision,
      onnx, coremltools; ruff and mypy for lint and type check).
    * Makefile with install / lint / test / bench / docs targets.
    * CI scaffolding under .github/workflows/.
    * No ML code yet. This release is the empty vessel.
